strings: <voice_0x01000BF3><se_low>January: ... you play like that? First he deceived us because of unfinished business, and then he came to save us.
<voice_0x01000BF4><se_def>China: I'm sorry if I cheated on you. These people don't believe me.
<voice_0x01000BF6><se_def>China: Who's to ask, Marcelo...he hates me.
<voice_0x01000BF7><se_def>China: So first I have to isolate him and then help him.
<voice_0x01000BF8><se_low>January: Alright, but you haven't known us since Adam.
<voice_0x01000BF9><se_low>January: Are we not afraid to befriend this old monster? Let's go
<voice_0x01000BFA><se_def>China: I don't really know anything about you, I wasn't there when they kidnapped her. But I do know he saved the priest's life.
<voice_0x01000BFB><se_def>China: Because the negative energy in the air vanished before you entered the interrogation room.
<voice_0x01000BFC><se_def>China: Then I'm not cool enough to leave you hanging on the floor.
<voice_0x01000BFD><se_def>China: I also hate it when women get into trouble. You know that Marcelo is an extremely talented researcher.
